Finally swept my EQ directory of screenshots.

http://www.mindspring.com/~rhoneyman/everquest

blackplate*.jpg Finally, all black, now I need a longsword and
shield.

azarack*.jpg All angles of the Azarack Island (full, 8 mobs)
Should help analysis of breaking it for those
who haven't done it yet.

And I forgot to take one of the named rat in DC, Jetsam I think his
name is. Lost the one of the girl with the Crown of Leaves too.

Harmonic, Bildge Hunter.
